ront/f/d/fd872395-f351-4f7e-9290-c34d1c98a567.jpg?1782752984"}, {"card": "Saiba Cryptomancer", "set": "MOM", "html": "&quot;Good luck getting through a class-seven proxy <mark>ward</mark>, creep.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/9/3934d535-740d-471a-bbf1-c3b26b1cd596.jpg?1782697775"}, {"card": "Bar the Door", "set": "DKA", "html": "&quot;It may not look like much, but it&#x27;s a good old door with strong <mark>wards</mark>. It&#x27;ll hold.&quot;\n—Olgard of the Skiltfolk", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/5/b593f544-2d82-4237-b9a9-88503b5036cc.jpg?1782714658"}, {"card": "Builder's Blessing", "set": "AVR", "html": "&quot;Mix the mortar with holy <mark>wards</mark>, or blood will run in the streets.&quot;\n—Vadvar, Thraben stonewright", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/a/2ad27af1-b482-40d5-9dbb-11201ffa0410.jpg?1782714546"}, {"card": "Scorchwalker", "set": "GTC", "html": "&quot;Borborygmos&#x27;s elemental launched an assault, but the Izzet <mark>wards</mark> held and experiments continue.&quot;\n—Skyknight report on the Rubblebelt", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/4/14ac6bde-1fef-45f4-b505-80a66b03140a.jpg?1782714109"}, {"card": "Barrier Breach", "set": "IKO", "html": "&quot;They cast <mark>wards</mark>, thinking it will protect them, but the biggest monsters find a way through.&quot;\n—Kinnan, bonder prodigy", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/2/822f8403-77a7-4e75-88af-60d604632f5d.jpg?1782707150"}, {"card": "Treefolk Mystic", "set": "ULG", "html": "Urza&#x27;s <mark>wards</mark> fell from him like autumn leaves as he entered the dreaming grove. He awoke imprisoned in living wood.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/6/9697acf5-9bc5-411d-8574-fe6185f18672.jpg?1782720561"}, {"card": "Relic Runner", "set": "2XM", "html": "Her knack for tampering with <mark>wards</mark> got her kicked out of the academy, but they also got her back in.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/b/fbced19d-7035-4284-93b3-cf2d4bcf9734.jpg?1782744012"}, {"card": "Lammastide Weave", "set": "LRW", "html": "&quot;A ribbon torn will <mark>ward</mark> away dark dreams.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/6/667fd7ab-de75-48e7-8d4b-a96130ae4666.jpg?1782716302"}, {"card": "Rune-Sealed Wall", "set": "FDN", "html": "&quot;If the giant, repelling <mark>wards</mark> aren&#x27;t enough to keep out nosy visitors, the huge wall should help.&quot;\n—Kastigan, reclusive runecaster", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/6/46674bd4-5160-44b2-bd2a-2da85c1e2697.jpg?1782683471"}, {"card": "Satoru, the Infiltrator", "set": "OTJ", "html": "&quot;This backwater doesn&#x27;t have a single wall, <mark>ward</mark>, or guard that could keep me out.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/c/acc9a5cc-2b3c-4c2f-8176-4a2d86265cc5.jpg?1782691959"}, {"card": "Silent Gravestone", "set": "RIX", "html": "Made to <mark>ward</mark> off the Grim Captain and silence the lure of undeath.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/f/ff60f685-a17e-4be6-bbb6-d14a053533ef.jpg?1782710208"}, {"card": "Gavony Township", "set": "MOC", "html": "&quot;The protective <mark>wards</mark> of the church have weakened, and no one can tell us why. It&#x27;s time to look to our own defenses.&quot;\n—Gregel, militia leader", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/e/ce46c4e2-a515-41d7-8d70-d20cf4925996.jpg?1782697864"}, {"card": "Manaplasm", "set": "CN2", "html": "Urak froze when he heard it. That was his first mistake. He turned and cast a dramatic <mark>ward</mark> spell. That was his last.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/3/439d3e7e-7c4f-4e1e-a95d-7ef44972d515.jpg?1782711685"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Tyranid Harridan", "set": "40K", "html": "Flying, <mark>ward</mark> {4}\nShrieking Gargoyles — Whenever this creature or another Tyranid you control deals combat damage to a player,